## 3. FREE CAR SPECIFICATION SOURCES

### 3.1 Truly Free Car APIs

| Source | URL | What It Offers | Free Tier | API Key |
|--------|-----|---------------|-----------|---------|
| **NHTSA vPIC API** | https://vpic.nhtsa.dot.gov/api/ | Official US government vehicle data. Makes, models, years, trims, body styles, engine, fuel type, safety ratings, VIN decoding. Covers all vehicles sold in the US. | Completely free. No rate limiting (within reason). No API key needed. | Not required |
| **CarQuery API** | http://www.carqueryapi.com/ | JSON-based API for year, make, model, trim data for cars and trucks. | Free (historically). Note: some Reddit reports indicate it may be unreliable/down. | Required (free signup) |

### 3.2 Free Tier / Freemium Car APIs

| Source | URL | What It Offers | Free Tier | API Key |
|--------|-----|---------------|-----------|---------|
| **API-Ninjas Cars API** | https://api-ninjas.com/api/cars | Thousands of vehicle models from 100+ automakers. Endpoints for makes, models, trims, detailed specs. Also has Electric Vehicle and Motorcycles APIs. | Free tier available BUT detailed endpoints (carmakes, carmodels, cartrims, cardetails) require Business/Professional subscription. Commercial use not permitted on free tier. | Required |
| **CarAPI.app** | https://carapi.app/ | Vehicle specs, VIN decoder, trim-level data. | Free tier exists | Required |

### 3.3 Open Car Datasets on GitHub

| Source | URL | What It Offers |
|--------|-----|---------------|
| **vbalagovic/cars-dataset** | https://github.com/vbalagovic/cars-dataset | 54,000+ vehicle variants across 370+ brands. Cars, trucks, motorcycles. 105,000+ real market price listings from 11 countries. |
| **abhionlyone/us-car-models-data** | https://github.com/abhionlyone/us-car-models-data | 15,000+ US car models from 1992-2026. |
| **plowman/open-vehicle-db** | https://github.com/plowman/open-vehicle-db | 69 makes with models/years/styles for cars, trucks, SUVs. |
| **ilyasozkurt/automobile-models-and-specs** | https://github.com/ilyasozkurt/automobile-models-and-specs | Manufacturers, models, engine options with specs. Updated Oct 2024. |
| **api-evangelist/car-api** | https://github.com/api-evangelist/car-api | Developer-friendly vehicle API and database. Makes, models, trims, bodies. |

**Recommendation for Cars**: Start with **NHTSA vPIC API** (completely free, no key, US government data). Supplement with **vbalagovic/cars-dataset** from GitHub for international coverage and price data. For non-US markets, the GitHub datasets fill gaps well.

