## 5. FREE PRICE / AFFILIATE DATA

| Source | URL | What It Offers | Free Tier | API Key |
|--------|-----|---------------|-----------|---------|
| **Amazon Product Advertising API 5.0** | https://webservices.amazon.com/paapi5/documentation/ | Product search, pricing, availability, images, customer reviews. Official Amazon affiliate integration. | API itself is free. Requires Amazon Associates membership. Rate: 1 request/day per $0.05 of shipped revenue (starts very low for new accounts). Must generate qualifying sales to maintain access. | Required (Amazon Associates account) |
| **Flipkart Affiliate API** | https://affiliate.flipkart.com/api-docs/af_prod_ref.html | Product feed, categories, pricing for Indian market. | Free with Flipkart affiliate membership. Affiliate program may be intermittently closed to new signups. | Required |
| **Kimovil** (scraping) | https://www.kimovil.com/ | Real-time prices from multiple retailers for phones. | No official API. Requires scraping. | N/A |
| **Datayuge Price Comparison API** | https://datayuge.com/products/price-comparison-api/ | Price comparison across Indian stores with affiliate commission. | Claims free tier available | Required |

**Key Limitation**: Amazon PA-API has strict requirements -- you must be an approved Amazon Associate AND generate qualifying sales to maintain API access. New accounts start with very low rate limits (1 TPD). This is the most common pain point for comparison sites.

**Recommendation**: Use Amazon PA-API if you already have an active Associates account. For price data without affiliate requirements, scrape Kimovil (for phones) or use the existing price data structure in your `data.js` pipeline.

